Uko umukino uri kugenda

17:27

Rayon Sports ishyizemo ikinyuranyo cy'amanota ane

Gutsinda uyu mukino bitumye Rayon Sports ikomeza kuyobora shampiyona n'amanota 66, aho irusha APR FC ya kabiri amanota ane, yo izakirwa na AS Muhanga kuri uyu wa Gatandatu.

Musanze FC yo igumye ku mwanya wa 12 n'amanota 32.

17:25

Umukino urarangiye: Rayon Sports itahanye amanota y'umunsi

Rayon Sports icyuye amanota y'umunsi wa 28 wa shampiyona waberaga kuri Stade ya Kigali, itsinze Musanze FC ibitego 3-1.

45' Igitego cya Musanze FC

36' Kwivuguruza k'umusifuzi Rulisa

15:57

15:54

21' Coup-franc ya Rayon Sports

15:52

18' Rayon Sports igerageje amahirwe

17' Rayon Sports ntabwo iribona mu mukino

Abakinnyi ba Rayon Sports barimo Ulimwengu Jules, Iradukunda Eric Radu na Donkor Prosper bari gukora amakosa atandukanye mu kibuga. Kugeza ubu iyi kipe nta mupira ukomeye iratera mu izamu ririmo Shema Innocent.

15:44

12' Mutsinzi atabaye Rayon Sports

Mugenzi Cedric azamukanye umupira mwiza iburyo, awuhindura mu izamu ukurwaho na Mutsinzi Ange ujya muri koruneri nyuma y'uko Kambale yari ategereje kuwushyira mu izamu. Bwari uburyo bwiza kuri Musanze FC iri kunyuzamo igasatira cyane muri iyi minota.

15:41

9' Umunyezamu wa Musanze FC agonganye na Ulimwengu

Munezero Fiston ananiwe gukuraho neza umupira wari utewe na Michael Sarpong,umunyezamu Shema Innocent azamuka mu kirere kuwufata agongana na Ulimwengu Jules ariko ahise ahaguruka. Uyu ni we munyezamu iyi kipe ifite gusa. Musanze FC ibonye uburyo bwiza imbere y'izamu, Mugenzi Cedrick ntiyagerera ku mupira igihe, uramusiga.

15:37

5' Rayon Sports itangiye kugumana umupira

Abakinnyi ba Rayon Sports b'inyuma no hagati barimo kugerageza guhererekanya umupira bashaka uko bagera kuri Michael Sarpong na Ulimwengu Jules kugeza ubu batarakora ku mupira.

15:34

2' Musanze FC irashaka aho imenera

Musanze FC itangiye umukino ishaka uburyo yabona izamu hakiri kare. Kaburuta na Kambale Salita Gentil bari gushaka inzira ariko ubwugarizi bwa Rayon Sports buhagaze neza.

15:32

Umukino uratangiye

Umusifuzi wo hagati, Rulisa, atangije umukino. Umupira wa mbere utewe na Musanze FC. Mugenzi Cedric arazamutse umusifuzi wo ku ruhande avuga ko habayeho kurarira.

15:14

Ibindi wamenya ku makipe yombi

Musanze FC yaje kuri uyu mukino ifite umunyezamu umwe, Shema Innocent. Mu gihe uyu munyezamu yagira ikibazo hakitabwa Gabiro wahoze wishyushya mukanya kashize. Iyi kipe ntabwo ifite kandi abarimo Kayigamba Jean Paul, Ndayisaba Olivier (barwaye) na Nduwayo Valeur ufite amakarita y'umuhondo atatu.

Rayon Sports ntabwo ifite Niyonzima Olivier 'Sefu' utaramera neza nyuma yo gukubitwa umupira ku mutwe, akagira isereri mu mukino uheruka kubera i Nyamagabe.

15:10

Icyo umukino uvuze ku makipe yombi

Rayon Sports irashaka gukomeza kuyobora shampiyona mu gihe hasigaye imikino itatu ikagera ku musozo. Iyi kipe iri ku isonga n'amanota 63, aho irusha APR FC ya kabiri inota rimwe gusa, yo izakirwa na AS Muhanga kuri uyu wa Gatandatu.

Musanze FC ya 12 n'amanota 32 ikeneye byibuze inota rimwe kugira ngo yizere kuguma mu cyiciro cya mbere.

14:49

Ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo

Tubahaye ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamiramboo hagiye kubera umukino w'umunsi wa 28 wa shampiyona hagati ya Rayon Sports na Musanze FC. Ni umukino ubimburiye iyindi mu gihe shampiyona igenda igana ku musozo.

Rayon Sports iheruka gukura amanota agoranye i Nyamagabe, itsinda Amagaju FC ibitego 2-1 mu gihe na Musanze FC yatsinze Sunrise FC mu buryo bugoranye, ibitego 2-1.
